# PATCH 011: reserve cold Copilot sessions during startup
#
# Prevents concurrent startup requests on the same execution session from
# billing multiple cold roots before the first successful response can mark
# the session warm. Keeps warmed-session noise intact while reducing bursts
# from OpenCode title-generation and similar parallel warm-up traffic.
